      "text": "Un tee aiswestĩ Behrni/\\\nas no ta Zeetuma btja nahku-\\\nchi/ uppureja Dedsamo-Lppu-\\\nus tam Israëka Deewam/ Di-\\\nvipadefmits Wehrſchũs preeſch\\\nwiſſũ Israëlu/ dewĩndefmits un\\\netchus Aunus/ ſeptĩndefmits\\\nn ſeptĩnus Zehrus/ diwipadet-\\\nnits Abſchũs par Grehku-Up-\\\nurt/ wiſſũ par Dedsamo-Up-\\\nurti tam KUNGAM.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pehz to dewe tee ta Keh-\\\nina Pawehleſchanas ta Kehni-\\\na Semmes-Walditajeem/ un\\\nWaldneekem ſchnipufs Lppes.\\\nIn tee pagohdeja tohs Laudis un\\\no Deewa Namnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta IX. Nodalla.\nſſraels fagahnahs pee Paganu Geewahm : 1.\\\nPar ko Eſruſſkumahs : 3. Luhds Deewu\\\nka teem Laudim tee Grehki peedohti tap-\\\ntu : 6.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ad nu ſchihs Leetas bt-\\\nja pabeigtas/ peegahje\\\npee manim tee Wirſuee-\\\ni/ un fazztja: Tee Israëka Lau-\\\ndis/ un tee Preestert un tee Le-\\\nviti/ ne irr attchkihrufchees no\\\nahs SeinmesLaudim/ (darri-\\\namĩ) pehz wiinu Neganti-\\\nahm/ no teem Kananiteeem/\\\nLetiteeem/Weresiteeem/ Jebu-\\\niteeem/ Ammoniteeem/ Moa-\\\niteeem/ Egiptereeem un Amo-\\\niteeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tee irr no winnu Met-\\\ntahm nehmuschi preeſch ſewim/\\\nun preeſch farweem Dehleen/ un\\\nirr fajaukuschi to ſwehtu Dsim-\\\nmunu ar teem Laudim tahs\\\nSeimmes/ un to Wirſneeku un\\\nWaldneeku Rohka irr ta pirma\\\nbijuſt eekich tchths Pahrkahp-\\\nschanas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad es nu ſcho Leetudsir-\\\ndeju/ tad ſaplohsjũ es ſawas\\\nDrehbes/ un ſawu Mehteli/ un\\\niſplehfu tohs Mattus no man-\\\nnas Galwas/ un mannas Bahr-\\\ndas/ un apſehdohs ſkunnigs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad ſapulzejahs pee man-\\\nnim wiſſi/ kas preeſch teem\\\nWahrdeem ta Israëka Deewa\\\ndrebbeja/ to Aiswestu Pahrkahp-\\\nschanas deht/ un es fehdeju ſkuun-\\\nmigs lihds Wakkara-Lppuxam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ap to Wakkara-Lppu-\\\nri zehlohß es no mannas Skum-\\\nschanas/ un ſaplohsjũ mannas\\\nDrehbes/ un mannu Mehteli/\\\nun es mettohs mannos Zeltõß/\\\nun iſplattiju mannas Rohkas\\\npreeſch to KUNGU mannu\\\nDeewu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es fazztju: Manu\\\nDeews/ es kaunohs/ un bihstohe\\\nmannu Waigu preeſch tewim\\\npazelt/ mans Deews/ jo muhſu\\\nNoseegumi irr watrojschees pahr\\\nmuhſo Galwn/ un muhſu Wah-\\\nna irr teela lihds Debbeſim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No muhſu Tehwu Dee-\\\nnahm eſſam mehs leela Noseegu-\\\nma/ lihds ſcho patchu Deenu/un\\\neſſam zaar muhſu Pahrkahp-\n"
    }
